	<div class="row g-5">
		<div class="col-md-7">
			<h2 class="text-body-emphasis outfit pb-3"><img src="~/images/mission.png" height="50px" width="50px"> Our Mission Statement</h2>
			<h5 class="text-body-emphasis outfit pb-3">CuraGo: A Doctor-Led, Doctor-Built Platform for Your Growth</h5>
			<p>
				At CuraGo, we understand the challenges doctors face, especially after years of hard work
				and dedication—feeling financially unrewarded is all too common. That’s why we’ve built a
				doctor-led platform designed to empower doctors like you to thrive. With our innovative
				at-home healthcare solution, you can earn more, work flexibly, and be in control of your
				practice, all while providing the highest quality care to your patients.
			</p>
			<h5 class="text-body-emphasis outfit pb-3">Why CuraGo?</h5>
			<p>
				<b>Built by Doctors for Doctors:</b> CuraGo is created by healthcare professionals who
				understand your needs. We’ve designed a platform that puts you at the center, offering the
				tools you need to maximize your income and career growth.
			</p>
			<p>
				<b>Earn More, Work Flexibly:</b> Provide high-quality, on-demand at-home healthcare, and earn
				more during off-hours, evenings, or weekends. Whether you're looking to supplement your
				income or shift to a more flexible schedule, CuraGo gives you that freedom. Flexibility is key,
				especially when you’ve already
				given so much to your patients.
			</p>
			<p>
				<b>Tech-Driven, Hassle-Free Logistics:</b> We handle appointment bookings, billing, and logistics,
				so you can focus on delivering care, growing your practice and what truly matters to you.
			</p>
			<p>
				<b>Financial and Leadership Growth:</b> Top performers can earn ESOPs and become partners in
				the company, gaining leadership roles in cities across India as we scale. It’s time your hard
				work pays off.
			</p>
			<p>
				<b>Affordable, Accessible Care:</b> We are committed to democratizing healthcare by making
				high-quality care affordable and accessible for all, while ensuring doctors like you are fairly
				compensated for your expertise.
			</p>
			<p>
				<b>A Cooperative of Doctors:</b> At CuraGo, we’re not just building a platform—we’re creating a
				network of doctors, where each one has a <b>potential</b> stake in our success. By joining CuraGo,
				you’re not just an employee; <b>you stand to become an owner</b>, contributing to something
				groundbreaking in healthcare. Together, we’re building a cooperative that brings ownership,
				shared growth, and the opportunity for doctors to thrive collectively.
			</p>
			<p class="fst-italic">
				If you’re looking for a platform that truly understands and values your contributions, CuraGo
				is here to change the way you practice medicine. Join us in building a better future for
				healthcare professionals and patients alike.
				Let’s revolutionize healthcare—together.
			</p>
			<p></p>	
		</div>
